cs3500.music.control

Interface KeyStrategy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, java.awt.event.KeyListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    KeyHandler

    public interface KeyStrategy
extends java.awt.event.KeyListener
    Interface to represent operations that must be performed by a key listener in the Music Editor program to handle user input. Allows a user to set their own strategies to handle keys.
